title: Facing Evil (Nekitta Hamilton, Davion Bishop and Faith Bisasor)
description:
A brutal crime scene… three lives lost… and forensic evidence in question… Here’s how a short trip to Florida changed a woman’s life forever.

For episode information and photos, please visit https://anatomyofmurder.com/.
